<% content_for :title, "Takedown & notices — Printwright" %>
<div class="container" style="max-width: 720px">
  <h1>Takedown &amp; rights notices</h1>
  <p class="t-small muted"><strong>Template process</strong> — testnet demonstration. Last updated 2026-07-17.</p>

  <p>If a model listed here infringes your rights, send a notice with:</p>
  <ol>
    <li>the model's URL and title;</li>
    <li>identification of the original work and your rights in it;</li>
    <li>a statement, under penalty of perjury, that the use is unauthorized;</li>
    <li>your contact details and signature.</li>
  </ol>
  <p>We remove the listing while we review (new sales stop immediately; certificates
    already anchored on-chain are immutable and record history, not endorsement). The
    designer is notified and may counter-notice with evidence of ownership — every
    published model carries a recorded ownership warranty from its designer, which is
    the accountability the certificate rail exists to provide.</p>
  <p>Send notices via the contact in the repository README.
    Repeat-infringer accounts are closed.</p>
</div>
